CustomField.description: Picklist to select Disbursement Channels as based on IATI codelist (http://reference.iatistandard.org/203/codelists/DisbursementChannel/). The code list sits in the API Name/value of the picklist value, while the Label is the human-readable name of the Disbursement Channel. This code is printed into the transaction/disbursement-channel/@code attribute in the IATI Activity XML.
CustomField.label: IATI Disbursement Channel
